        </param>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Spawns <computeroutput>exe</computeroutput> with <computeroutput>args</computeroutput> as a detached child process and returns immediately. The child survives this process exiting (Windows: DETACHED_PROCESS; POSIX: setsid + double-fork). Returns true if the child was launched successfully (does not verify it then ran to completion). </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
